{
  "stem": "11722.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 88.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "At the time, we were about maybe 3,000 to 5,000 of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "We marched.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "It was difficult to go on the road with these wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "The snow clung to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "It's just like walking on skates.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Anybody who twisted an ankle and couldn't continue was shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "Anybody who tried to escape was shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After about three days, we-- we-- three nights, we walked and slept in fives.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "The three in the middle slept, and two on the-- on the outside were walking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "And you can sleep and walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "It's amazing how much a human being can endure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "I remember one time we stopped in a-- on a farm, in a big barn.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "Everybody piled in, and we piled up on top of one another.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "All those who were on the bottom probably suffocated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "People were taking off clothes from the dead, from one another, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] trying to change shoes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "Anybody who lost a cap, you know, grabbed somebody else's cap.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "People were fending for themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We became worse [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] than animals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] We finally arrived in a camp called Blechhammer, and the guards left us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the gate was open.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "Some of us wandered out into the woods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "One time, I remember we found out where the warehouse was, and we just went as a group and tried to break the door open.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "And we went in there, and we just brought all the foodstuff out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "And people were just fighting, scratching.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "And I remember suddenly there was a machine gun erected opposite.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "And they started machine-gunning us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "This friend of mine and I-- who I had befriended, another French boy-- we were buddy-buddy.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
